Place_Leave_Rosemary.Text: Wait, where are you going? There might be something else in here!

Interact_Door-Frame.Text: This door frame is made of nice wood...

Interact_Outlet_Occupied.Text: Just a regular power outlet. There's a cord plugged in to it.

Interact_Speaker_Initial.Text: Why would you need that here?

Interact_Speaker.Text: How many of these does this place have?

Interact_Air-Vent.Text: So that's how they're pumping oxygen throughout the station.

Interact_Restroom_Mirror.Text: There's a mirror on the wall.

Interact_Restroom_Sink.Text: At least I know I can keep my hands clean.

Interact_Stairs_Up.Text: These stairs must go up to the next floor.

Interact_Stairs_Down.Text: These stairs must go down to the lower floor.

Interact_Bookcase_Empty.Text: It looks like a bookcase, but it's empty.

Interact_Shelf_Empty.Text: A metal wire shelf. There's nothing on it.

Interact_Desk_Corner.Text: A desk sits in the corner of the room.

Interact_Desk-Chair.Text: A chair sits in front of the desk.

Interact_Trash-Can_Stacked.Text: Some empty trash cans are stacked together.

Interact_Chair_Stacked.Text: There are some chairs stacked in the corner.

Interact_File-Cabinet.Text: A file cabinet. It has 4 drawers.

Interact_Cabinets_Wall.Text: There are cabinets mounted on the wall. Maybe there's something inside of them?

Interact_Refrigerator.Text: It looks like a large refrigerator.

Interact_Table_Metal.Text: There's a shiny industrial-looking metal table.
